                    <span>This is probably one of the best books for learning software testing techniques. If you are new to software testing and don't have a "mentor" to teach you the techniques I would recommend this book, then check out some of the modern structured "risk-based" testing process books, such as Testing IT by John Watkins to get up-to-date on what has changed in the testing world since 1992.</span>
                  
              
